    <title>New release for Postiz: New Feature: Sets</title>
    <updated>2025-06-09T11:12:56-04:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>gitroomhq/postiz-app</name>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;p&gt;You can now create Sets in the settings page.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sets let you create a template of the workflow of the post, &lt;strong&gt;for example&lt;/strong&gt;:
You can create a set containing all your default personal accounts and add some settings.
When you create a new post, you can choose the set, and it will automatically turn everything on based on what you specified.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;More Examples:
- Set for a customer
- Set for personal accounts
- Set for business accounts&lt;/p&gt;</content>
